 CHARMM>    stream step3_packing_pol.str
 VOPEN> Attempting to open::step3_packing_pol.str::
 OPNLGU> Unit 99 opened for READONLY access to step3_packing_pol.str

                    INPUT STREAM SWITCHING TO UNIT    99
 RDTITL> * TOPOLOGY AND PARAMETERS FOR A BIG-SPHERE (POL)
 RDTITL> *
 Parameter: IN1 <- "" <empty>
  
 CHARMM>     
  
 CHARMM>    !if you rtf does not have the following mass, you have to add it
 CHARMM>    !MASS 250    POLO 30.97400   ! Fake lipid sphere
 CHARMM>     
  
 CHARMM>    read rtf card append
 MAINIO> Residue topology file being read from unit  99.
 RDTITL> * RTF FOR POL
 RDTITL> *

      ***** LEVEL  1 WARNING FROM <rtfrdr> *****
